{"tid":2149613,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"世紀公投 陶傑 vs 蕭若元 邊個有料d？","createTime":"2020-08-10T13:19:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T09:35:00.000Z","uid":157483,"like":252,"dislike":114,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"03988c81ad5602fcccd3817b32ee822bda88f65e","tid":2149613,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:19:30.000Z","msg":"眾所週知，兩個人係世紀宿敵 不斷隔空揶揄對方垃圾、冇學識、假大空、欺世盜名等等<br />\n經歷語錄：<br />\n蕭若元：<br />\n陶傑係一個文妓，係連小學既常識都可以搞錯 哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈。欺世盜名莫過於此。 好 最近我地d韓牛.....<br />\n我抆條鳩毛都粗過陶傑大脾啊！哈哈哈哈哈哈<br />\n<br />\n陶傑：我唔會去回應d我唔識既人講我既野，可能有d人個節目冇咩收視 要借我黎令多d人睇囉<br />\n對唔住，佢要同我辯論我都嫌佢未夠班啊<br />\n<br />\n正評：陶傑有料d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評：蕭生有料d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39aa47124d61301d2252e1e2c920099ffaa8ac56","tid":2149613,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:23:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bcb40eea5349c1f3072823dcc8a875ee4c1785","tid":2149613,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"暫時才子領先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168436443f1ffd15f04b94f009ea087f7461d0a3","tid":2149613,"uid":259302,"like":8,"dislike":13,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:30:03.000Z","msg":"投黃毓民一票"},{"pid":"631a2f435613f294333137adb0cfd692b66021c1","tid":2149613,"uid":157483,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:30:49.000Z","msg":"暫時才子領先，但sample未夠大，大家繼續踴躍投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab97ca109c1a3b9023fc1e9cf3a821a2a8617ae","tid":2149613,"uid":157483,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"168436443f1ffd15f04b94f009ea087f7461d0a3","tid":2149613,"uid":259302,"like":8,"dislike":13,"score":-5,"cited